  "text": "The App will require access to microphones. The user will be asked to grant access to this when the application is first launched. Users often grant such access as they rarely question the necessity of these requests [CITATION_1] . In addition, the App might be designed such that this permission seems reasonable to the user. For example, the App might have sound effects and offer voice control.",
